caption: Liked this place's duck salad called Mancha. I'm addicted to it.

A great place for some good old fashion comfort food. They can turn a simple grill cheese sandwich into the most delicious, mouth watering grill cheese sandwich that you will ever taste. With three various cheeses combined with garlic on a brioche bun, the oil and butters that oozes off the bread is stellar. The taste is there.
Good selection,  maybe a little limited.  A little pricey. Really Friendly service, and some wines that go wonderfully with the cheese.  Ill go back to explore the wines and some fun pairings

Incredibly polite team here. Love their sandwiches. Quite an improvement over local sandwich and hogs grease shops. Great bread, great ingredients and great combos. Simple menu. Keep up the great quality. And yes, they are incredibly fast.

Went here for breakfast and I think I'm in love! The staff here are so knowledgeable and friendly. The sandwich they made was amazing. I only wished I lived closer, I'd visit more often. Thanks guys - it was great!

Wonderful sandwich place serving up flavorful salads, sandwiches, grilled cheeses and drinks. Their menu is based on recipes or dishes from French speaking countries. When I'm looking for a mildly healthy lunch, I swing by here for one of their sandos. It's a relatively quick order and the staff is great.
A little slice of France in the heart of the financial district.

very delicious. i had a cousin come into town and asked me to take him back here.

Great way to enjoy a bit of France in San Francisco, including the charming smiles and french accents.  The menu is great for lunch and a late afternoon snack or happy hour.  Very nice selection of cheese too!

This place is a gem. Friendly staff, tasty sandwiches and salads. I come here once a week for lunch and appreciate the authentic French touch from the owners. They have a wide selection of cheeses and wines so great place to visit before office parties downtown. I hope they open up a location in the East Bay! Merci Beaucoup.
